<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10437816>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Collected specimens. Gerromorpha, Gerridae. A. Brachymetra albinervus, apterous male from São Fidélis, Rio de Janeiro (−21.6106, −41.8078). B. Cylindrostethus palmaris, apterous male from Silva Jardim, Rio de Janeiro (−22.4997, −42.2662). C. Limnogonus aduncus aduncus, macropterous male from Pimenta, Minas Gerais (−20.6664, −45.8344). Scale bars: 2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10437816/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10437818>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Distribution in southeastern Brazil and adjacent areas. A. Brachymetra albinervus. B. Cylindrostethus palmaris. C. Limnogonus aduncus aduncus. Stars indicate new records; circles indicate previous records." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10437818/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

